	<h1 class="title">这样的曝光方式让特朗普在 Instagram 很受欢迎</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马宁忆 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-07 15:38:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23415/medium/23415.jpg?1457333123" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


